# SoA Data-Oriented Vector
# Uses: Shape (#), Allocation (new), Set (set), Get (get)

# Define 3D Vector Shape
# Vector3 x y z
# Vector3 i64 i64 i64

# Define a function to initialize a vector at index 0
: init_vec n
    let v new Vector3 > ^0
    set & v x 0 10
    set & v y 0 20
    set & v z 0 30
    get > v x 0
